><br>Please stop in and give greetings, comments and suggestions.<br><br>Fair journey to you all,<br> <p><p><b>Arminya<br>ezOP<br><a href="http://pub92.ezboard.com/beverquestroleplayers">EverQuest Roleplayers</a></b></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/uarminya.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arminya</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>New to the block</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(6/10/02 8:25:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm10.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=118.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: EverQuest Role-players</span><hr size=1> The board is now fully open for posting!!<br><br>We want everyone that is interested in role-playing within EQ to become regular contributors to the board. Guild leaders of role-playing guilds and their members are highly encouraged. Together we can help each other keep the life that role-playing adds to the game.<br><br><br><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><center> <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><u>Our Goals</u><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END--></center><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br><br><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> *To preserve the art of RPing on all servers of EQ.<br><br>*To provide a place for RPers to discuss game mechanics, RPing events, RPing ideas, and stories.<br><br>*To give RPing guilds, their leaders/officers, and individuals, resources, and assistance in regards to RPing within the game.<br><br>*To assist RPing guilds with common issues regarding alignments, classes, factions and game mechanical/design stumbling blocks within EQ.<br><br>*To encourage each other to keep the faith and have a great time RPing.</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br><br><br>Visit us at:<br><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub92.ezboard.com/beverquestroleplayers">pub92.ezboard.com/beverquestroleplayers</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> <